original_title: Saint Patrick's Day Event Celebration Live 2022
overview: After the unseen footage of the tragedy that was 'Saint Patrick's Day Event Celebration Live 2021', the dynamic duo, Jan and Cody return to throw the greatest Saint Patrick's Day event in history, all within the confines of Cody's new apartment living room.
tagline: His grandson Todd just bought him an Ipad today.
